author: Warhammer
description:
Owlcat Games, alongside the launch of the Alpha, presents the new Gameplay Trailer for the upcoming Warhammer 40,000: Dark Heresy. Become an acolyte of the Inquisition in this grimdark, party-based, story-driven cRPG. Lead investigations, uncover grand conspiracies, master tactical combat, and wage a secret war against heresy. Learn more about Warhammer 40,000: Dark Heresy at https://darkheresy.owlcat.games/
